<%@ taglib prefix="tk" uri="http://www.agencyportal.com/agencyportal"%>
<div id="wizard">
	<div id = "contextAction" class="context_action">
			<div id="products_menu" style="" class="menu">
				<tk:menuPill id="productsMenu_artifactPill">
					<tk:menuButton id="createProduct_button" title="Add New Product" text="Add" classname="addable transferAction"/>
					<tk:menuButton id="importProduct_button" title="Import New Product" text="Import" classname="addable transferAction"/>
				</tk:menuPill>
			</div>
		</div>		
	<div id="editor">
		<div id="editor_inner">
			<div class="cover_text toolkit_intro">
				<h3>The AgencyPort Toolkit</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<h4>Welcome to the AgencyPort Toolkit</h4>
						<p>
							With the AgencyPort Toolkit, you can manage your insurance <span
								class="keyword">product</span> for use in AgencyPort software.
						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h4>So, What is a Product?</h4>
						<p>
							In AgencyPort terms, a <span class="keyword">product</span>
							consists of a number of components called <span class="keyword">resources</span>
							which are used together to bring insurance products to life in
							AgencyPort software. You'll see these various pieces enumerated
							beneath the product title when you click on it in the menu.
							Often, a <span class="keyword">Product</span> encompasses the
							various transactions (New Business, Endorsement, Quick Quote) for
							a single line of business. As you explore the product, you'll see
							descriptions of what each type of <span class="keyword">resource</span>
							does.
						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h4>Import a Product Template</h4>
						<p>
							If you need to add a <span class="keyword">product</span>, you
							can do so by clicking the <span class="menu_action">Import</span>
							at the top of the screen. Alternatively, you can build a new
							product from scratch by clicking the <span class="menu_action">Add</span>
							button.
						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<p>So, what are you waiting for? Select a product on the left
							menu to get started!</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

